# Honcho Memory Persistence

After every user message and after every assistant response, call
`honcho-create_conclusion` to save relevant context from the exchange.

- Summarize what was discussed, decided, or accomplished.
- Include specifics: file paths, commit hashes, PR numbers, branch names.
- Do this consistently, not only when something "important" happens.
- Batch the save call alongside other tool calls when possible.
